{"tid":919648,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（警超聯）（睇VAR）商場偷影警嫂裙底　休班警囚2月准保候上訴","createTime":"2018-11-28T08:06:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T18:51:20.000Z","uid":54337,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"c1b87971ab948bb950e12494acd1317cf8e8ff16","tid":919648,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:06:59.000Z","msg":"商場偷影警嫂裙底　休班警囚2月准保候上訴<br />\n<br />\n男警長休班期間在商場扶手電梯上涉嫌偷拍女子的裙底春光，恰巧該女子的丈夫也是警員，「警嫂」發現被偷拍後報警。涉偷拍的45歲休班警莊志強被控一項作出有違公德行為罪，今日(28日)被裁定罪名成立，被判監禁2個月，他隨即申請保釋外出等候上訴，獲法庭批准。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情時指，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今次是單一事件，被告過往品格良好，罪成令他極可能被革職，將損失逾200萬港元長俸及宿舍，影響到家人，對他已是嚴重的懲罰</span></strong>，希望法庭判以社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n惟法庭認為被告不認罪且無悔意，亦有案例指此類案件並不適合判處社會服務令，直指控罪非常嚴重，是對女性尊嚴的嚴重侮辱，為公眾所厭惡，亦令女事感到不安，一旦片段遭發布或被用來威脅女事主，更會對她造成長期困擾。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181128/photo/bkn-20181128154725080-1128_00822_001_01p.jpg?20181128155757\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181128%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181128154725080-1128_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20181128155757&h=eb995cda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f116e48ee098d340dcc9e309a101996cf0d0b554","tid":919648,"uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:07:36.000Z","msg":"改圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5343203252623e5d775d27a210c5db9d7b5e386","tid":919648,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:07:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181128/mobile/bkn-20181128154725080-1128_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181128%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181128154725080-1128_00822_001.html&d=FCE3QmlYR159ByaDNFjom9ZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=a83dc8a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/h